Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.04,OP_E,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Sick with justice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:26.93,OP_E,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I just wanna feel you
